N2  - The article presents officer election results at different division meetings of the Academy of Management. The article announces the election results for the Eastern Division meetings held April 14?15, 1967; the results include Walter Hill as President, C. Wickham Skinner as President-elect, and Robert Schellenberger as Vice President. The article also announces election results for the Western Division meeting on March 16?18, 1967 and the Midwest Division on April 7?8, 1967.
